Name: The Two of Us
About the game: The Two of Us is a 2D Co-op Platformer that has a strong emphasis on working together. You will be greeted with various puzzle levels where you must work in conjunction with your friend to navigate the level. The game is complete with 2D Animations, Sound Effects and PvE Combat.
